==Urdu==
===Etymology===
From Sanskrit [[विडाली]].
===Noun===
'''{{URchar|بلّی}}''' (billī) {{f}} ({{m}}: '''{{URchar|بلّا}}''')
# [[cat]]

====Devanagari spelling====
*[[बिल्ली]]

====Usage notes====
*Although this word is feminine and used for female ''cats'', it is also used to mean ''domestic cat'' in general.  The masculine form, or the word for tomcat, is '''{{URchar|بلّا}}''' (billā).

